channel.title: NooliesKnickKnacks – Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War
channel.description: Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War is a first-person shooter video game developed by Treyarch and Raven Software and published by Activision. r/BlackOpsColdWar is a developer-recognized community focused on the title.

item.title: I liked the new teaser for the zombies map forsaken so much that I decided to print it for fun. Thought it might look cool up on my refrigerator!
item.dc:creator: NooliesKnickKnacks
